db.sqlCmd: BEGIN TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL REPEATABLE READ
SELECT TXID_CURRENT() AS txid, PG_BACKEND_PID() AS pid, NOW() AS tx_now

WITH req_ids AS ( SELECT DISTINCT auh."assetUsageReqId" FROM "assetUsageHistory" AS auh WHERE auh."softwareLicensorId" = ($1)) SELECT aur."assetUsageType", aur."response" FROM "assetUsageReq" AS aur, req_ids WHERE aur."assetUsageReqId" = req_ids."assetUsageReqId" ORDER BY COALESCE((aur."response"->>'requested')::TIMESTAMPTZ, aur."requestStarted"), aur."assetUsageReqId"
